name: Horimon 003 龍:DRAGON
description:
Meaning : Spiritual Strength, Power, Success, Protection

In Chinese mythology, only the few carps which reach the dragon gate at the top of the waterfall can become a dragon. This makes the dragon tattoo a symbol of success. The dragon rising into the sky (looking up) means great success, and the dragon descending from the sky (looking down) means it will protect you and your family from any bad luck.
